        "subject": "LU-19620 tests: skip sanity/60b interop for old clients",
        "message": "LU-19620 tests: skip sanity/60b interop for old clients\n\nSanity test_60b is counting llog messages to the console to check\nif console message ratelimiting is working.  More (valid) messages\nwere added to test_60a and the \"reasonable\" number of messages is\nlarger.  Skip this if running on an old client with lower limit.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: 63ee4af3bb (\"LU-19620 obdclass: llog to continue if broken\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: Ia7558068a4324ad074672b186e1cfb1398f978c9\n"
